Class MinContainer<T extends java.lang.Object & java.lang.Comparable<? super T>>

  • java.lang.Object

    T - The type of object to be contained, must extend Comparable

    public class MinContainer<T extends java.lang.Object & java.lang.Comparable<? super T>>
extends java.lang.Object
    An extension of the HashSet implementation, with a reference to a minimum element in the set.
